wiki.text:
'Nucleus' may refer to: *Atomic nucleus, the very dense region at the center of
an atom *Cell nucleus, the control center of a cell, containing the cell's
chromosomal DNA *Nucleus (neuroanatomy), a cluster of neurons in the central
nervous system *Nucleus (syllable), the central part of a syllable in
linguistics *Comet nucleus, the solid, central part of a comet *Condensation
nucleus, the seed of a raindrop **Ice nucleus, the seed of a snowflake
